<h3>LinkedIn Does Not Work For</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Restaurants, cafes, and food businesses</strong> (use Instagram and <a href="/blog/optimize-google-business-profile/">Google Business Profile</a> instead)</li>
<li><strong>Retail stores</strong> (Instagram and Facebook drive consumer foot traffic)</li>
<li><strong>Salons and beauty businesses</strong> (visual platforms outperform LinkedIn)</li>
<li><strong>Home service contractors</strong> (plumbers, electricians, HVAC) (Facebook and Nextdoor are better)</li>
