<p>The distinction is simple. If your customer is a business owner, executive, or professional making B2B purchasing decisions, LinkedIn is essential. If your customer is a consumer making personal spending decisions, <a href="/best/best-social-media-platforms-local-businesses/">other platforms work better</a>.</p>
